      • getJavascriptChartName

        public String getJavascriptChartName()
        Description copied from class: BaseEvent
        Returns the name of the javascript variable holding the Highcharts "chart" object. The name of this variable can be used to create custom javascript on the server side when an event is fired via AJAX. The so created javascript can then be executed on the client.
        Overrides:
        getJavascriptChartName in class BaseEvent
        Returns:
        the name of the javascript variable holding the Highcharts "chart" object.
